These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, chef
There are 2 different nationalities: german, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, motorbike
1. the chef is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
2. the journalist is on the right of the chef##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | cola    |
| Job           | chef | journalist |
| Nationality   | german       | thai  |
| Transport     | van      | motorbike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: orange, pepper
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, country
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, bike
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | pepper | orange |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep       | country         |
| Pet           | snake     | hedgehog         |
| Transport     | bike    | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, paramedic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, metal
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, skateboard
1. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the police-officer##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking          | baking |
| Job           | paramedic | police-officer     |
| Music-Genre   | techno            | metal         |
| Transport     | skateboard         | van   |

