The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, zombie
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, funk
2 different pets are kept: horse, pony
1. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | crime |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | funk |
| Pet           | horse | pony    |

