.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, cucumber
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, blues
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, van
1. the fan of blues is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person eating cabbage is the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of classical is the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | tea     | water |
| Food          | cucumber   | cabbage |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | classical     |
| Transport     | subway | van     |

 